abstract: At South Street Seaport, a old-fashioned printing house has returned to business after a hiatus, still using some of the same techniques Benjamin Franklin used.
snippet: At South Street Seaport, a old-fashioned printing house has returned to business after a hiatus, still using some of the same techniques Benjamin Franklin used.
lead_paragraph: The first thing about Robert Warner's print shop is it is urine-free.

headline.main: A Print Shop Cranks Back Up, Ancient as Ever
